&lt;p&gt;Welcome to the UQ Python User Group (UQ PUG). We meet monthly, and our next gathering is on the 6th of March. We meet in room 12-N109 (Central Library).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section id="about-us" class="level2"&gt;
&lt;h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="about-us"&gt;About us&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;section id="who-are-we" class="level3"&gt;
&lt;h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="who-are-we"&gt;Who are we?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;UQ PUG is a &lt;strong&gt;gathering for Python users of any proficiency&lt;/strong&gt;, to help each other solve problems, share resources and tips, discover new features and hang out as a friendly community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;section id="when-do-we-meet" class="level3"&gt;
&lt;h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="when-do-we-meet"&gt;When do we meet?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Every &lt;strong&gt;first Thursday of the month&lt;/strong&gt; from &lt;strong&gt;10:00 am&lt;/strong&gt; to 11:30am&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In-person at UQ Central Library 12-N109&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Find the next gathering on the &lt;a href="https://web.library.uq.edu.au/library-services/training#keyword=Python%20User%20Group;campus=;weekstart="&gt;UQ Library Training Page&lt;/a&gt; and book in through StudentHub&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contact us at &lt;a href="mailto:training@library.uq.edu.au"&gt;training@library.uq.edu.au&lt;/a&gt; for any questions or support&lt;/li&gt;
